---
title: Per-artifact architecture — universal click dispatch
---
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant SrcComp as Source component<br/>(any: PrepareEditor,<br/>JsonViewer, ListPage,<br/>etc.)
  participant Resolver as Generic Resolver
  participant Registries as registries
  participant TgtComp as Target component<br/>(picked by kind)

  User->>SrcComp: clicks a reference<br/>(symbol in code body,<br/>value in tree, name in list)
  Note over SrcComp: locate the matching ref<br/>SymbolRef by line/col<br/>(in CodeBodySpec) or<br/>by JSON Pointer<br/>(in JsonSchemaWithRefs),<br/>or an ArtifactRef<br/>(prompt_name, tools[i], table)
  SrcComp->>Resolver: (kind, name)
  Resolver->>Registries: registries[kind][name]
  Registries-->>Resolver: ArtifactRegistration.spec
  Resolver->>Resolver: COMPONENT_BY_KIND[kind]
  Resolver->>TgtComp: render(spec)
  TgtComp-->>User: shown<br/>(modal, side panel,<br/>page nav, hover preview, …)
